description: This file is a C header file (.h) that declares the interface for the Slap Owo Loac object in the Service Logic Aggregation Plane implementation. It contains function prototypes, licensing, and module information, but no actual function implementations or class definitions.

methods.name: SlapCreateOwoLoac
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Owo Loac object with specified container, owner, and reservation handles.

methods.name: SlapOwoLoacCreate
methods.description: Creates an Owo Loac object with specified container, owner, and reservation handles.

methods.name: SlapOwoLoacEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects into the Owo Loac instance.
